</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="13" pageNumber="14" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Because of the severe deforestation over the last 100 years in the area where this species was found, it is likely it is now extinct or at least with a much smaller range.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
